data.description: Welcome to your new home in McDonough, GA! This stunning 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom single-family home is situated on approximately 1 acre of land with the added bonus of NO HOA, offering you the perfect blend of space, privacy, and freedom. As you approach the home, you'll be captivated by the charming rocking chair front porch a the ideal spot to savor your morning coffee while surrounded by the tranquility of nature. The two-story entry foyer welcomes you with large windows and a vaulted ceiling, creating a bright and airy atmosphere. Step into the spacious living room featuring a stone fireplace, providing a cozy and inviting space. The well-appointed kitchen includes a breakfast bar with seating, eat-in breakfast area, pantry, and ample counter and cabinet space. The dining area with bay window is open to the kitchen and living room and includes picturesque views of the property. The main-level primary bedroom with en suite is tucked away making it a true private retreat. Two additional bedrooms, another full bath, and a large laundry room complete the main level, providing convenience and functionality. Venture upstairs to discover a haven for guests or family members with two large bedrooms, a spacious walk-in closet, a full bath, and an open loft area that can be customized to suit your needs. Hard-surface flooring throughout the main level adds an elegant touch, while plush carpeting upstairs provides comfort and warmth. Step outside to the rear deck and take in the expansive fenced backyard, complete with a storage building for added convenience. The 2-car garage ensures ample space for your vehicles and storage needs. This McDonough gem offers a perfect blend of modern amenities and serene surroundings, providing a lifestyle that's both comfortable and convenient. Don't miss the opportunity to make this 5-bedroom beauty your forever home. Schedule a showing today and experience the unique charm and spacious living that this McDonough residence has to offer!
